# Tools & Utils Rules

Dynamic Tailwind classes → always use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`.

Before adding new helpers:
- Check `src/utils/`
- Do not duplicate logic from `src/lib/utils.ts`

Reuse:
@/utils/time  
@/utils/string